title: Canton of Argentat-sur-Dordogne
text: The <a href="cantons%20of%20France">canton</a> of Argentat-sur-Dordogne (before March 2020: "Argentat") is an administrative division situated in the Corrèze département and in the <a href="Nouvelle-Aquitaine">Nouvelle-Aquitaine</a> region of France.
